rogue-like game
===============

*Working only on Unix-like systems

The game is under development and doesn't have a name yet.
Already has a random room generation, now working on core mechanics.

Build:
```
	cd src
	make
```

Movement:  hjkl, HJKL
Inventory: i*
Drop:      d
Wield:     w
Wear:      W
Quaff:     q
Go to next level: >

Symbols:
@ - playable character
B - beast, unfriendly npc
: - loot
# - wall
+ - door
" - path
> - thing that move to next level
< - thing you came from
